    <item>
      <title>Các tính năng mới trong ES6</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/es6-features/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/es6-features/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;các-tính-năng-mới-trong-es6&#34;&gt;Các tính năng mới trong ES6&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;ES6 (ECMAScript 2015) là một phiên bản quan trọng của JavaScript, giới thiệu nhiều tính năng mới giúp code trở nên clean và powerful hơn.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;1-let-và-const&#34;&gt;1. let và const&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Thay thế var với scope tốt hơn:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-javascript&#34; data-lang=&#34;javascript&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;// var có function scope&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;example&lt;/span&gt;() {&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;) {&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;var&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;x&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    }&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;x&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;// 10&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;}&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;// let và const có block scope&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;example&lt;/span&gt;() {&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;) {&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;y&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;z&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;20&lt;/span&gt;;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    }&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;y&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;// ReferenceError&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;z&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;// ReferenceError&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;}&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;2-arrow-functions&#34;&gt;2. Arrow Functions&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Cú pháp ngắn gọn cho function:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Cú pháp cơ bản trong Java</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/cu-phap-co-ban-java/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/cu-phap-co-ban-java/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;cú-pháp-cơ-bản-trong-java&#34;&gt;Cú pháp cơ bản trong Java&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Để bắt đầu lập trình với Java, bạn cần hiểu các cú pháp cơ bản. Bài viết này sẽ giới thiệu những khái niệm nền tảng.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;cấu-trúc-chương-trình-java&#34;&gt;Cấu trúc chương trình Java&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Một chương trình Java đơn giản nhất có cấu trúc như sau:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-java&#34; data-lang=&#34;java&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;HelloWorld&lt;/span&gt; {&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;void&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;main&lt;/span&gt;(String&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;[]&lt;/span&gt; args) {&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        System.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;out&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;println&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Hello, World!&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    }&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;}&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;các-thành-phần-cơ-bản&#34;&gt;Các thành phần cơ bản&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;1-class-và-object&#34;&gt;1. Class và Object&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Class&lt;/strong&gt;: Là blueprint cho object.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Object&lt;/strong&gt;: Instance của class.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;2-biến-và-kiểu-dữ-liệu&#34;&gt;2. Biến và kiểu dữ liệu&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Java có các kiểu dữ liệu nguyên thủy:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Framework Java: Spring Boot</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/frameworks-java-spring/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/frameworks-java-spring/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;framework-java-spring-boot&#34;&gt;Framework Java: Spring Boot&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Spring Boot là một framework Java phổ biến nhất cho việc phát triển ứng dụng enterprise. Nó giúp đơn giản hóa việc tạo ứng dụng Spring độc lập, production-ready.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;spring-boot-là-gì&#34;&gt;Spring Boot là gì?&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Spring Boot là một extension của Spring Framework, được thiết kế để giảm thiểu configuration và cho phép developer tập trung vào business logic.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;lợi-ích-chính&#34;&gt;Lợi ích chính&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;1-auto-configuration&#34;&gt;1. Auto Configuration&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Spring Boot tự động cấu hình ứng dụng dựa trên dependencies trong pom.xml.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Framework JavaScript: React</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/frameworks-js-react/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/frameworks-js-react/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;framework-javascript-react&#34;&gt;Framework JavaScript: React&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;React là một thư viện JavaScript phổ biến nhất cho việc xây dựng user interface. Được phát triển bởi Facebook, React tập trung vào việc tạo reusable UI components.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;react-là-gì&#34;&gt;React là gì?&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;React là một thư viện JavaScript declarative, efficient, và flexible để xây dựng user interfaces. Nó cho phép developer tạo complex UIs từ small và isolated pieces of code gọi là &amp;ldquo;components&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;đặc-điểm-nổi-bật&#34;&gt;Đặc điểm nổi bật&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;1-component-based&#34;&gt;1. Component-Based&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;UI được chia thành các components nhỏ, reusable.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Giới thiệu về Java</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/gioi-thieu-java/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/gioi-thieu-java/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;giới-thiệu-về-java&#34;&gt;Giới thiệu về Java&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Java là một ngôn ngữ lập trình hướng đối tượng, được phát triển bởi Sun Microsystems (nay là Oracle) vào năm 1995. Java được thiết kế để có thể &amp;ldquo;viết một lần, chạy mọi nơi&amp;rdquo; (Write Once, Run Anywhere - WORA), nhờ vào máy ảo Java (JVM).&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;lịch-sử-phát-triển&#34;&gt;Lịch sử phát triển&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Java được tạo ra bởi James Gosling và nhóm của ông tại Sun Microsystems. Ban đầu, Java được gọi là Oak, nhưng sau đó được đổi tên thành Java. Java được phát hành chính thức vào năm 1995.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>JavaScript là gì?</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/javascript-la-gi/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/javascript-la-gi/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;javascript-là-gì&#34;&gt;JavaScript là gì?&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;JavaScript là một ngôn ngữ lập trình kịch bản (scripting language) được sử dụng chủ yếu để tạo trang web tương tác. JavaScript chạy trên trình duyệt web và cho phép developer thêm động lực và tương tác vào trang web tĩnh.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;lịch-sử-phát-triển&#34;&gt;Lịch sử phát triển&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;JavaScript được tạo ra bởi Brendan Eich tại Netscape vào năm 1995. Ban đầu được gọi là Mocha, sau đó đổi thành LiveScript, và cuối cùng là JavaScript. Mặc dù có tên &amp;ldquo;Java&amp;rdquo; nhưng JavaScript không liên quan đến Java.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Lập trình hướng đối tượng trong Java</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/lap-trinh-huong-doi-tuong-java/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/lap-trinh-huong-doi-tuong-java/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;lập-trình-hướng-đối-tượng-trong-java&#34;&gt;Lập trình hướng đối tượng trong Java&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Lập trình hướng đối tượng (OOP) là một paradigm lập trình dựa trên khái niệm &amp;ldquo;object&amp;rdquo;. Java là một ngôn ngữ OOP thuần túy, hỗ trợ đầy đủ các tính chất của OOP.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;4-tính-chất-chính-của-oop&#34;&gt;4 tính chất chính của OOP&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;1-encapsulation-đóng-gói&#34;&gt;1. Encapsulation (Đóng gói)&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Ẩn dữ liệu và chỉ cho phép truy cập thông qua methods public.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-java&#34; data-lang=&#34;java&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;Student&lt;/span&gt; {&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;private&lt;/span&gt; String name;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; String &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;getName&lt;/span&gt;() {&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; name;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    }&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;void&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;setName&lt;/span&gt;(String name) {&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;name&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; name;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    }&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;}&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;2-inheritance-kế-thừa&#34;&gt;2. Inheritance (Kế thừa)&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Cho phép một class kế thừa thuộc tính và method từ class khác.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>So sánh Java và JavaScript</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/so-sanh-java-va-javascript/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/so-sanh-java-va-javascript/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;so-sánh-java-và-javascript&#34;&gt;So sánh Java và JavaScript&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Mặc dù có tên giống nhau, Java và JavaScript là hai ngôn ngữ lập trình hoàn toàn khác nhau. Bài viết này sẽ so sánh chúng về nhiều khía cạnh.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;nguồn-gốc&#34;&gt;Nguồn gốc&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Java&lt;/strong&gt;: Được phát triển bởi Sun Microsystems (Oracle) vào 1995&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;JavaScript&lt;/strong&gt;: Được tạo ra bởi Brendan Eich tại Netscape vào 1995&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;kiểu-ngôn-ngữ&#34;&gt;Kiểu ngôn ngữ&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Java&lt;/strong&gt;: Compiled language, strongly typed&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;JavaScript&lt;/strong&gt;: Interpreted language, dynamically typed&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;thực-thi&#34;&gt;Thực thi&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Java&lt;/strong&gt;: Chạy trên JVM (Java Virtual Machine)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;JavaScript&lt;/strong&gt;: Chạy trên JavaScript engine (V8, SpiderMonkey, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;cú-pháp&#34;&gt;Cú pháp&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;java&#34;&gt;Java&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-java&#34; data-lang=&#34;java&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;HelloWorld&lt;/span&gt; {&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;void&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;main&lt;/span&gt;(String&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;[]&lt;/span&gt; args) {&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        System.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;out&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;println&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Hello, World!&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    }&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;}&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;javascript&#34;&gt;JavaScript&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-javascript&#34; data-lang=&#34;javascript&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Hello, World!&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;kiểu-dữ-liệu&#34;&gt;Kiểu dữ liệu&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;java-1&#34;&gt;Java&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Primitive types: int, double, boolean, char&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Reference types: String, arrays, objects&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;javascript-1&#34;&gt;JavaScript&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Primitive: number, string, boolean, undefined, null, symbol, bigint&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Objects và functions&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;oop&#34;&gt;OOP&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;java-2&#34;&gt;Java&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Class-based OOP&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Strong encapsulation&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Inheritance, polymorphism, abstraction&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;javascript-2&#34;&gt;JavaScript&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Prototype-based OOP&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Flexible object creation&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;ES6 classes (syntactic sugar)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;sử-dụng&#34;&gt;Sử dụng&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;java-3&#34;&gt;Java&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Enterprise applications&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Android apps&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Big data processing&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Desktop applications&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;javascript-3&#34;&gt;JavaScript&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Web development (frontend &amp;amp; backend)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Mobile apps (React Native)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Game development&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;IoT&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;performance&#34;&gt;Performance&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Java&lt;/strong&gt;: Generally faster, compiled to bytecode&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;JavaScript&lt;/strong&gt;: Interpreted, nhưng engines hiện đại rất nhanh&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;learning-curve&#34;&gt;Learning Curve&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Java&lt;/strong&gt;: Dốc hơn, nhiều concepts cần học&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;JavaScript&lt;/strong&gt;: Dễ bắt đầu, nhưng có nhiều &amp;ldquo;gotchas&amp;rdquo;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;ecosystem&#34;&gt;Ecosystem&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Java&lt;/strong&gt;: Maven, Spring, Hibernate, etc.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;JavaScript&lt;/strong&gt;: npm, React, Vue, Node.js, Express&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;khi-nào-dùng-java&#34;&gt;Khi nào dùng Java?&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Large-scale enterprise applications&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;High-performance computing&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Android development&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Khi cần type safety và performance&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;khi-nào-dùng-javascript&#34;&gt;Khi nào dùng JavaScript?&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Web development&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Rapid prototyping&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Real-time applications&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Khi cần flexibility và quick development&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Cả hai ngôn ngữ đều có vị trí quan trọng trong ngành công nghiệp phần mềm, và việc học cả hai sẽ mở ra nhiều cơ hội nghề nghiệp.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Thao tác DOM với JavaScript</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/dom-manipulation-javascript/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/dom-manipulation-javascript/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;thao-tác-dom-với-javascript&#34;&gt;Thao tác DOM với JavaScript&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;DOM (Document Object Model) là một API cho phép JavaScript tương tác với HTML và CSS. DOM manipulation là kỹ năng cốt lõi để tạo trang web động.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;dom-là-gì&#34;&gt;DOM là gì?&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;DOM là một cấu trúc dạng cây đại diện cho cấu trúc của tài liệu HTML. Mỗi element HTML trở thành một node trong cây DOM.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;các-phương-thức-chọn-element&#34;&gt;Các phương thức chọn element&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;1-getelementbyid&#34;&gt;1. getElementById()&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-javascript&#34; data-lang=&#34;javascript&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;element&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; document.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;getElementById&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;myId&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;2-getelementsbyclassname&#34;&gt;2. getElementsByClassName()&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-javascript&#34; data-lang=&#34;javascript&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;elements&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; document.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;getElementsByClassName&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;myClass&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;3-getelementsbytagname&#34;&gt;3. getElementsByTagName()&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-javascript&#34; data-lang=&#34;javascript&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;elements&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; document.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;getElementsByTagName&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;div&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;4-queryselector-và-queryselectorall&#34;&gt;4. querySelector() và querySelectorAll()&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-javascript&#34; data-lang=&#34;javascript&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;element&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; document.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;querySelector&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;#myId .myClass&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;elements&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; document.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;querySelectorAll&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;.myClass&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;thay-đổi-nội-dung&#34;&gt;Thay đổi nội dung&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;1-innerhtml&#34;&gt;1. innerHTML&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-javascript&#34; data-lang=&#34;javascript&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;element&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;innerHTML&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;New content&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;2-textcontent&#34;&gt;2. textContent&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-javascript&#34; data-lang=&#34;javascript&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;element&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;textContent&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;New text content&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;3-innertext&#34;&gt;3. innerText&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-javascript&#34; data-lang=&#34;javascript&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;element&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;innerText&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;New text&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;thay-đổi-style&#34;&gt;Thay đổi style&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-javascript&#34; data-lang=&#34;javascript&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;element&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;style&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;color&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;red&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;element&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;style&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;fontSize&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;20px&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;element&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;classList&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;add&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;newClass&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;element&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;classList&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;remove&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;oldClass&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;tạo-và-thêm-element&#34;&gt;Tạo và thêm element&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-javascript&#34; data-lang=&#34;javascript&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;newElement&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; document.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;createElement&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;div&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;newElement&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;textContent&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;New element&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;document.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;body&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;appendChild&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;newElement&lt;/span&gt;);&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;sự-kiện-events&#34;&gt;Sự kiện (Events)&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-javascript&#34; data-lang=&#34;javascript&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;element&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;addEventListener&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;click&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt;() {&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Element clicked!&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;});&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;ví-dụ-thực-tế&#34;&gt;Ví dụ thực tế&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-javascript&#34; data-lang=&#34;javascript&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;// Tạo todo list động&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;addTodo&lt;/span&gt;() {&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;todoText&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; document.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;getElementById&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;todoInput&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;).&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;value&lt;/span&gt;